where m  is the mass of the particle and v its speed.", "fibs": ["wave"]}
{"text": "Equation (11.5) is known as the de Broglie relation and the wavelength λ of the matter wave is called de Broglie wavelength.", "fibs": ["Equation"]}
{"text": "The dual aspect of matter is evident in the de Broglie relation.", "fibs": ["aspect"]}
{"text": "On the left hand side of Eq.", "fibs": ["hand"]}
